pageContext.claim: “We have many, many companies coming in to the United States. They're coming in, car companies, they're going into Michigan and Ohio and all over.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump suggests that Mexican jobs are leaving for the United States. In reality, Chrysler is shifting truck production to the United States, but not at the expense of jobs or plants in Mexico. The Mexicans keep their jobs, while new ones will be created in the United States.
